snippet.title: VESSELED - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
VESSELED is a short 3D horror game where you switch from being able to see your surroundings to moving around, exploring a weird reality in an effort to find a way out.

Get the game here - https://electrodev.itch.io/vesseled

Join my DIscord: https://discord.gg/KRfvxPTtP7
Follow me on Twitter: https://twitter.com/EIectroDev
